      • timeCode

        public final long timeCode
        Code execution time (millis) for execution. Measures the time taken to execute the R code for execution.

        Can be used in conjunction with timeStart and timeTotal to profile execution runtime characteristics.

      • timeTotal

        public final long timeTotal
        Total time (millis) for execution. Measures the time taken to prepare R workspace and directory for execution, execute R code and then persist execution artifacts to on project.

        Can be used in conjunction with timeStart and timeCode to profile execution runtime characteristics.
